{"tid":2271773,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警察拘港台記者查車牌之際 申訴專員調查入境處拒《蘋果》查婚姻紀錄","createTime":"2020-11-04T17:28:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-05T00:36:31.000Z","uid":240362,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a0f409e3f5815c7d2f02dfc75273aba332eee9e8","tid":2271773,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T17:28:40.000Z","msg":"查冊是傳媒查證真相的重要工具，政府卻逐步收窄查冊空間，警察甚至以虛報查閱車牌目的為由，拘捕追查7.21元朗恐襲警黑勾結真相的港台《鏗鏘集》編導蔡玉玲。除運輸署修改查冊「申請用途」外，去年入境處亦突然收緊出生及結婚紀錄的查冊規定，拒絕《蘋果》記者查冊申請。《蘋果》早前向申訴專員公署投訴，公署報告引述入境處指，傳媒可以公眾利益為由申請查冊，但記者其後再以傳媒身份申請卻再遭拒絕；《蘋果》就此再向公署投訴，公署今日回覆表示將進行全面調查。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》記者於去年10月底在入境處轄下婚姻登記事務及紀錄辦事處申請翻查「香港結婚紀錄」，獲告知該處於同月已更改了查冊安排，任何人查閱他人的出生或結婚紀錄，需獲當事人授權，否則要提供合理原因供入境處審批。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201104/CIZR7TNWXBC5ZOAANNAWW7YCUE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201104%2FCIZR7TNWXBC5ZOAANNAWW7YCUE%2F&d=t9lvrop9ljT%2F%2Fon6qZ%2B%2FxsRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=5a73d212\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201104%2FCIZR7TNWXBC5ZOAANNAWW7YCUE%2F&h=6c5c1dee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201104/CIZR7TNWXBC5ZOAANNAWW7YCUE/</a>"},{"pid":"c6c20f521a207ba25110ca5991e1fc239e94386d","tid":2271773,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T17:29:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"651e2c4741c985f8a6f215819f6beb4eb36fa12c","tid":2271773,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T17:35:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/n